"To simplify compilation, we use <literal>pkg-config</literal>, which is present in all (properly installed) <application>gtkmm</application> installations. "
"This program 'knows' what compiler switches are needed to compile programs that use <application>gtkmm</application>. The <literal>--cflags</literal> "
