msgid ""
"The <classname>ComboBox</classname> widget offers a list (or tree) of choices in a dropdown menu. If appropriate, it can show extra information about each "
"item, such as text, a picture, a check button, or a progress bar. The <classname>ComboBox</classname> widget usually restricts the user to the available "
