#. (itstool) path: section/para
#: C/index-in.docbook:4951
msgid ""
"If you try to draw one pixel wide lines, you may notice that the line sometimes comes up blurred and wider than it ought to be. This happens because Cairo "
"will try to draw from the selected position, to both sides (half to each), so if you're positioned right on the intersection of the pixels, and want a one "
