#. (itstool) path: chapter/para
#: C/index-in.docbook:6850
msgid ""
"Although you can use <phrase role=\"nowrap\">C++</phrase> code to instantiate and arrange widgets, this can soon become tedious and repetitive. And it "
"requires a recompilation to show changes. The <link xlink:href=\"https://gitlab.gnome.org/jpu/cambalache\">Cambalache</link> application allows you to "
