#. (itstool) path: chapter/para
#: C/index-in.docbook:7656
msgid ""
"<application>gtkmm</application> makes it very easy to derive new widgets by inheriting from an existing widget class, either by deriving from a container "
"and adding child widgets, or by deriving from a single-item widget, and changing its behavior. But you might occasionally find that no suitable starting "
